    48→    48→/**
    49→    49→ * GET /pm/schedule
    50→    50→ *
    51→    51→ * List PM schedules with filtering and pagination.
    52→    52→ *
    53→    53→ * Query Parameters:
    54→    54→ * - trainId: Filter by train
    55→    55→ * - depotId: Filter by assigned depot
    56→    56→ * - pmTypeId: Filter by PM type
    57→    57→ * - status: Filter by status (SCHEDULED, IN_PROGRESS, COMPLETED, DEFERRED, CANCELLED)
    58→    58→ * - fromDate: Target date from (inclusive)
