   146→   146→ *
   147→   147→ * Get proposed man-hour adjustments with filtering.
   148→   148→ *
   149→   149→ * Query Parameters:
   150→   150→ * - status: Filter by status (PROPOSED, APPROVED, REJECTED, APPLIED)
