    39→    39→
    40→    40→/**
    41→    41→ * GET /baselines
    42→    42→ *
    43→    43→ * List plan baselines with filtering and pagination.
    44→    44→ *
    45→    45→ * Query Parameters:
    46→    46→ * - status: Filter by status (DRAFT, PUBLISHED, SUPERSEDED, ARCHIVED)
    47→    47→ * - fromDate: Filter by baseline date (ISO date)
