    53→    53→ * Query Parameters:
    54→    54→ * - status: Filter by status (ACTIVE, PROMOTED, DISCARDED, EXPIRED)
    55→    55→ * - createdBy: Filter by creator user ID
    56→    56→ * - forkedFromBaselineId: Filter by source baseline
    57→    57→ * - forkedFromScenarioId: Filter by source scenario
    58→    58→ * - includeExpired: Include expired scenarios (default: false)
    59→    59→ * - page: Page number (default: 1)
    60→    60→ * - pageSize: Items per page (default: 20, max: 100)
    61→    61→ * - sort: Sort field (name:asc, createdAt:desc, lastModifiedAt:desc, expiresAt:asc)
